{"tid":2232161,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人同我一樣好怕死","createTime":"2020-10-06T07:58:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T00:29:16.000Z","uid":217842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"326fa753f90a126afd2b4270f14a4c8815ed3798","tid":2232161,"uid":217842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T07:58:40.000Z","msg":"由細到大 我都有好多irrational fears<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如細個有試過一次鎖埋咗廁所門之後開幾次先開到<br />\n從此之後我甚至有段時間去廁所唔敢鎖門<br />\n<br />\n去到而家我呢排突然好怕死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實由細到大都間唔中會 但係呢排翻發<br />\n<br />\n覺得人生最多100 年對比起呢個世界上億年歷史好短暫<br />\n好驚好快去多終點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢排係無時無刻都會有panic attack 會作嘔同埋成個人好唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 甚至夜晚訓唔著 會驚以後醒唔翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上網睇啲安慰自己嘅嘢越睇越唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無人可以開解吓我<br />\n或者我係咪應該去睇吓psychologist"},{"pid":"1020b02d4c8520426bf4b48c792a356124d06a43","tid":2232161,"uid":232250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T07:59:51.000Z","msg":"年齡？<br />\n<br />\n我越來越怕死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：三十尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dedec0e99d125d39c30efc8ad32fea697e5e53b","tid":2232161,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T08:01:16.000Z","msg":"死啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d2c42fe519962c555ff8d666382bd4c82150880","tid":2232161,"uid":1582,"like":3,"disli